{"type": "article", "id": 2227, "title": "乐高建筑系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:09:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222257H0kw8zgOKDbZyP5c.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">乐高积木一直以那些五彩缤纷的塑料小方块而著称，但全新的乐高建筑系列玩具再次证明这家公司拓展成年人市场的野心。The Lego Architecture Studio 系列让你不是专业设计师也能拼出类似设计工作室的那些炫酷又带着未来感的建筑原型（Prototype）。超过 1200 块积木、76 个独一无二的组件，包括那些侧边带有凹槽的乐高积木，方便人们使用在建筑中发挥想像力。厚厚的 250 页的说明书也被做成了手绘图纸的风格，据说马岩松也参与了这套乐高积木的研发。新的乐高建筑系列定价 159.99 美元，</span><a href=\"http://shop.lego.com/en-US/Studio-21050\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135113AzNTtgHxG0wij3be.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135114G9h6baQrTIxRUvzw.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135114WJbnPYpDyI1rBhOT.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"392\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61298701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135115agxd6IXDzTNOGQZt.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"392\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61298701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135115v4MCkryp3aNPYwLS.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"392\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61298701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}